ys\u0142awa Strzemskiego przez \u017co\u0142nierzy b. Zwi\u0105zku Radzieckiego. (S 6/02/Zk)] Polish [[Institute of National Remembrance]]. Internet Archive, 16.10.03. Retrieved 16 July 2007.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Justice and the Genesis of War\">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=i2Z5blE1KGoC&pg=PA148&lpg=PA148&dq=May+23+Hitler+lebensraum|title=Justice and the Genesis of War|isbn=978-0-521-55868-6|last1=Welch|first1=David A.|date=25 August 1995}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Krivosheev\">\u041a\u0440\u0438\u0432\u043e\u0448\u0435\u0435\u0432 \u0413. \u0424., ''\u0420\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0438\u044f \u0438 \u0421\u0421\u0421\u0420 \u0432 \u0432\u043e\u0439\u043d\u0430\u0445 XX \u0432\u0435\u043a\u0430: \u043f\u043e\u0442\u0435\u0440\u0438 \u0432\u043e\u043e\u0440\u0443\u0436\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044b\u0445 \u0441\u0438\u043b. \u0421\u0442\u0430\u0442\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0438\u0447\u0435\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0435 \u0438\u0441\u0441\u043b\u0435\u0434\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435'' (Krivosheev G.F., ''Russia and the USSR in the wars of the 20th century: losses of the Armed Forces. A Statistical Study'' Greenhill 1997 {{ISBN|1-85367-280-7}}) {{in lang|ru}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Nazi Loss in Poland Placed at 290,000\">{{cite web|title=Nazi Loss in Poland Placed at 290,000 |website=The New York Times |year=1941 |url=http://www.freeimagehosting.net/image.php?cdbae543be.jpg |accessdate=16 January 2009 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207150102/http://www.freeimagehosting.net/image.php?cdbae543be.jpg |archivedate=7 February 2009 |df= }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PN\">{{cite book | last = Peszke | first = Michael Alfred | authorlink = Michael Alfred Peszke | title = Poland's Navy, 1918\u20131945 | publisher=[[Hippocrene Books]] | date = February 1999 | isbn = 978-0-7818-0672-5| page = 37}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Poland's Holocaust: Ethnic Strife, Collaboration with Occupying Forces and Genocide...\">{{cite book |author=Tadeusz Piotrowski |title=Poland's 