]]'' (1936)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Good Thief (film)|The Good Thief]]'' (2002)\n| ''[[Bob le flambeur]]'' (1956)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Grand Seduction]]'' (2013)\n| ''[[Seducing Doctor Lewis]]'' (2003, Canada)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Gunman (2015 film)|The Gunman]]'' (2015)\n| ''[[Le choc]]'' (1982)\n| The novel ''The Prone Gunman'' ([[Jean-Patrick Manchette]])\n|-\n| ''[[The Guv'nor (film)|The Guv'nor]]'' (1935)\n| ''Rothchild'' (1933)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Gypsy Melody]]'' (1936)\n| ''[[Juanita (1935 film)|Juanita]]'' (1935)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Happy New Year (1987 film)|Happy New Year]]'' (1987)\n| ''[[La bonne ann\u00e9e]]'' (1973)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Heartbeat (1946 film)|Heartbeat]]'' (1946)\n| ''[[Beating Heart (film)|Battement de coeur]]'' (1940)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Hell's Cargo]]'' (1939)\n| ''[[Alert in the Mediterranean|Alerte en M\u00e9diterran\u00e9e]]'' (1938)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Human Desire]]'' (1954)\n| ''[[La B\u00eate Humaine (film)|La B\u00eate Humaine]]'' (1938)\n| The novel ''[[La B\u00eate humaine]]'' ([[\u00c9mile Zola]])\n|-\n| ''[[Intersection (1994 film)|Intersection]]'' (1994)\n| ''[[The Things of Life|Les choses de la vie]]'' (1970)\n| The novel ''Les choses de la vie'' ([[Paul Guimard]])\n|-\n| ''[[I Think I Love My Wife]]'' (2007)\n| ''[[Love in the Afternoon (1972 film)|L'Amour l'apr\u00e8s-midi]]'' (1972)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[I Was an Adventuress]]'' (1940)\n| ''{{Interlanguage link multi|I Was an Adventuress (1938 film)|J'\u00e9tais une aventuri\u00e8re|fr}}'' (1938)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Journal of a Crime]]'' (1934)\n| ''Une vie perdue'' (1933)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Jungle 2 Jungle]]'' (1997)\n| ''[[Un indien dans la ville]]'' (1994)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Just My Luck (1933 film)|Just My Luck]]'' (1933)\n| ''Aza\u00efs'' (1932)\n| The play ''Aza\u00efs ([[Fifty-Fifty (play)|Fifty-Fifty]])''\n|-\n| ''[[Just Visiting (film)|Just Visiting]]'' (2001)\n| ''[[Les Visiteurs]]'' (1993)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[A Kind of Murder]]'' (2016)\n| ''[[Enough Rope (film)|Le Meurtrier]]'' (1963)\n| The novel ''[[The Blundere