]]'' (1960) \n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Postman Always Rings Twice (1946 film)|The Postman Always Rings Twice]]'' (1946)\n| ''[[Ossessione]]'' (1943)\n| The novel ''The Postman Always Rings Twice'' ([[James M. Cain]])\n|-\n| ''[[The Postman Always Rings Twice (1981 film)|The Postman Always Rings Twice]]'' (1981)\n| ''[[Ossessione]]'' (1943)\n| The novel ''The Postman Always Rings Twice'' ([[James M. Cain]])\n|-\n| ''[[Scent of a Woman (1992 film)|Scent of a Woman]]'' (1992)\n| ''[[Scent of a Woman (1974 film)|Profumo di donna]]'' (1974)\n| The novel ''Il buio e il miele'' ([[Giovanni Arpino]])\n|-\n| ''[[Sweet Charity (film)|Sweet Charity]]'' (1969)\n| ''[[Le Notti di Cabiria]]'' (1957)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Swept Away (2002 film)|Swept Away]]'' (2002)\n| ''[[Swept Away (1974 film)|Travolti da un insolito destino nell'azzurro mare d'agosto]]'' (1974)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[A Walk in the Clouds]]'' (1995) \n| ''[[Quattro passi fra le nuvole]]'' (1942)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Welcome to Collinwood]]'' (2002) \n| ''[[Big Deal on Madonna Street|I Soliti Ignoti]]'' (1958)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Which Way Is Up?]]'' (1977)\n| ''[[Mim\u00ec metallurgico ferito nell'onore]]'' (1972)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Wild Is the Wind]]'' (1957)\n| ''[[Fury (1947 film)|Furia]]'' (1947)\n|\n|}\n\n== Japanese ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! English-language film\n! Japanese-language film\n! Common source material (if any)\n|-\n| ''[[Apartment 1303 3D]]'' (2012)\n| ''[[Apartment 1303]]'' (2007)\n| The novel ''Apartment 1303'' (Kei Oishi)\n|-\n| ''[[Alita: Battle Angel]]'' (2019)\n| ''[[Battle Angel (OVA)|Battle Angel]]'' (1993)\n| The manga  [[\u9283\u5922]] (Gunnm) by [[Yukito Kishiro]]\n|-\n| ''[[Battle Beyond the Stars]]'' (1980)\n| ''[[Seven Samurai]]'' (1954)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Dark Water (2005 film)|Dark Water]]'' (2005)\n| ''[[Dark Water (2002 film)|Dark Water]]'' (2002)\n| The short story \"[[Dark Water (book)|Floating Water]]\" ([[Koji Suzuki (writer)|Koji Suzuki]])\n|- <!--\n\n\"Django\" (1966) is an Italian-language film without American actors.\n\n-->\n|-\n| ''[[Death Note (2017 film)|Death Note]]'' (2017)\n| ''[[Death Note (2006 film)|Death Note]]'' (2006)\n| The manga ''[[Death Note]]''\n|-\n| ''Don't Look Up'' (2009)\n| ''[[Don't Look Up]]'' (1996)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Eight Below]]'' (2006)\n| ''[[Antarctica (1983 film)|Antarctica]]'' (1983)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[A Fistful of Dollars]]'' (1964)\n| ''[[Yojimbo]]'' (1961)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Ghost in the Shell (2017 film)|Ghost in the Shell]]'' (2017)\n| ''[[Ghost in the Shell (1995 film)|Ghost in the Shell]]'' (1995)\n| The manga ''[[Ghost in the Shell (manga)|Ghost in the Shell]]'' ([[Masamune Shirow]])\n|-\n| ''[[Godzilla (1998 film)|Godzilla]]'' (1998)\n| ''[[Godzilla (1954 film)|Gojira]]'' (1954)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Godzilla (2014 film)|Godzilla]]'' (2014)\n| ''[[Godzilla (1954 film)|Gojira]]'' (1954)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Grudge]]'' (2004)\n| ''[[Ju-On: The Grudge]]'' (2002)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Grudge (2020 film)|The Grudge]]'' (2020)\n| ''[[Ju-On: The Grudge]]'' (2002)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Guardian (2006 film)|The Guardian]]'' (2006)\n| ''[[Umizaru (film)|Umizaru]]'' (2004)\n|  \n|-\n| ''[[Hachi: A Dog's Tale]]'' (2010)\n| ''[[Hachiko Monogatari]]'' (1987)\n|\n|-\n| ''Iron Maze'' (1991)<!--Director: Hiroaki Yoshida; Starring: Jeff Fahey, Bridget Fonda, Hiroaki Murakami-->\n| ''[[Rashomon]]'' (1950)\n| The short stories \"[[Rash\u014dmon (short story)|Rash\u014dmon]]\" and \"[[In a Grove]]\" ([[Ry\u016bnosuke Akutagawa]])\n|-\n| ''[[Last Man Standing (1996 film)|Last Man Standing]]'' (1996)\n| ''[[Yojimbo]]'' (1961)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Magnificent Seven]]'' (1960)\n| ''[[Seven Samurai]]'' (1954)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Magnificent Seven (2016 film)|The Magnificent Seven]]'' (2016)\n| ''[[Seven Samurai]]'' (1954)\n|-\n| ''[[Midnight Sun (2018 film)|Midnight Sun]]'' (2018)\n| ''[[A Song to the Sun|Midnight Sun]]'' (2006)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[One Missed Call (2008 film)|One Missed Call]]'' (2008)\n| ''[[One Missed Call (2003 film)|Chakushin Ari]]'' (2003)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Outrage]]'' (1964)\n| ''[[Rashomon]]'' (1950)\n| The short stories \"[[Rash\u014dmon (short story)|Rash\u014dmon]]\" and \"[[In a Grove]]\" ([[Ry\u016bnosuke Akutagawa]])\n|-\n| ''[[Pulse (2006 film)|Pulse]]'' (2006)\n| ''[[Pulse (2001 film)|Kairo]]'' (2001)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Ring (2002 film)|The Ring]]'' (2002)\n| ''[[Ring (film)|Ring]]'' (1998)\n| The novel ''[[Ring (Suzuki novel)|Ring]]'' ([[Koji Suzuki (writer)|Koji Suzuki]])\n|-\n| ''[[The Secret (2007 film)|The Secret]]'' (2007)\n| ''[[Himitsu (film)|Himitsu]]'' (1999)\n| The novel ''[[Naoko (novel)|Naoko]]'' ([[Keigo Higashino]])\n|-\n| ''[[Shall We Dance? (2004 film)|Shall We Dance?]]'' (2004)\n| ''[[Shall We Dance? (1996 film)|Shall We Dance?]]'' (1996)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Warrior and the Sorceress]]'' (1984)\n| ''[[Yojimbo]]'' (1961)\n|  \n|-\n| ''[[The Yellow Handkerchief (2008 film)|The Yellow Handkerchief]]'' (2008)\n| ''[[The Yellow Handkerchief (1977 film)|The Yellow Handkerchief]]'' (1977)\n|  \n|}\n\n== Korean ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! English-language film\n! Korean-language film\n! Common source material (if any)\n|-\n| ''[[Galgameth|The Adventures of Galgameth]]'' (1996)\n| ''[[Pulgasari]]'' (1985, North Korea)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Compulsion (2013 film)|Compulsion]]'' (2013)\n| ''[[301, 302]]'' (1995)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Lake House (film)|The Lake House]]'' (2006)\n| ''[[Il Mare]]'' (2000)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Mirrors (film)|Mirrors]]'' (2008)\n| ''[[Into the Mirror]]'' (2003)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[My Sassy Girl (2008 film)|My Sassy Girl]]'' (2008)\n| ''[[My Sassy Girl]]'' (2001)\n| The novel ''My Sassy Girl'' (Kim Ho-sik)\n|-\n| ''[[Oldboy (2013 film)|Oldboy]]'' (2013)\n| ''[[Oldboy (2003 film)|Oldboy]]'' (2003)\n| The manga ''[[Old Boy (manga)|Old Boy]]'' ([[Nobuaki Minegishi]], [[Garon Tsuchiya]])\n|-\n| ''[[Possession (2009 film)|Possession]]'' (2009)\n| ''[[Addicted (2002 film)|Addicted]]'' (2002)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Uninvited (2009 film)|The Uninvited]]'' (2009)\n| ''[[A Tale of Two Sisters]]'' (2003)\n| The fo